{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"TextDecoder: fatal property","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/fatal","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.TextDecoder.fatal"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API\">Encoding API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/encoding\"><code>encoding</code></a></li><li><em><code>fatal</code> </em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/ignoreBOM\"><code>ignoreBOM</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/decode\"><code>decode()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Encoding API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>fatal</code></strong> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a> interface is a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> indicating whether the error mode is fatal.</p>\n<p>\n  If the property is <code>true</code>, then a decoder will throw a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a> if it encounters malformed data while decoding.\n  If <code>false</code>, the decoder will substitute the invalid data with the replacement character <code>U+FFFD</code> (�).\n  The value of the property is set in the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder()</code> constructor</a>.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  A boolean which will be <code>true</code> if the error mode is set to <code>fatal</code>.\n  Otherwise, it will be <code>false</code>, indicating that the error mode is <code>replacement</code>.\n</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/#ref-for-dom-textdecoder-fatal①","title":"Encoding Standard"}],"query":"api.TextDecoder.fatal"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.TextDecoder.fatal"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The fatal read-only property of the TextDecoder interface is a Boolean indicating whether the error mode is fatal.","popularity":0,"modified":"2023-04-08T06:16:25.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/textdecoder/fatal","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/textdecoder/fatal/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/0c8a320b035cf625c1df67713a94ead2e7f3aec6","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"fatal","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder","title":"TextDecoder"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder/fatal","title":"fatal"}]